ActExport Development Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of KARNA GUPTA of Oakville, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Export Development Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jeffrey Steiner, whose term has expired.
